title: Noreaga in full support of Kanye West's 2020 Presidential campaign, but can't vote
text:
Rapper Victor Santiago aka Noreaga is going to be Kanye West's biggest supporter when he runs for 2020 Presidential campaign , but he will not be able to vote.
READ: Kanye West performs 12 extra hours of community service
Listen to Kanye West on Gaana.com
Noreaga told TMZ that he was going to be Kanye's biggest supporter when he runs for President, however, added that he cannot vote because he was a felon. The 38-year-old rapper said that he is going to make everyone, he knows, vote for Kanye.
